WESTERN SOUTH ATLANTIC.
URUGUAY.
1. SEISMIC SURVEY 28 AND 29 MAR BY M/V RAMFORM VANGUARD
   TOWING 12 7000 METER LONG CABLES
   ALONG TRACKLINES BETWEEN:
   A. 34-49.53S 052-33.98W AND 35-29.43S 051-31.57W.

2. CANCEL THIS MSG 30 MAR 13.
